            . I hold a situation in the Bank. On Sunday, the 1st of July, I was at <placeName id="t18320705-253-crimeloc1325">Holborn-bars</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320705-253-crimeloc1325" type="placeName" value="Holborn-bars"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320705-253-crimeloc1325" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-253-off1324 t18320705-253-crimeloc1325"></join>, at a quarter before twelve o'clock at night - I felt my handkerchief taken - I turned, and seized the prisoner with it in his hand; I gave him to the officer, but I saw him run from him, and I held him till the officer came up again and took him - I understood the officer had been knocked down and had lost the handkerchief; and while I stood there I was surrounded by thirty or forty bad characters.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was ten yards from the gentleman when he took me, and I was ill-used by the Policeman.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18320705-253-verdict1326" type="verdictDescription">
